  "content": "<p data-pid=\"ggInGgIr\">针对阅读和完形填空，确实可以这样做。这是快速扩大词汇量的捷径。</p><p data-pid=\"-2NPi9Xm\">我当初也做过类似的事情，将高中词汇分成三个部分：</p><ol><li data-pid=\"MbrKT4fD\">阅读词汇</li><li data-pid=\"FQksV_Xz\">语用词汇</li><li data-pid=\"3pD-yiSs\">写作词汇</li></ol><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-79b74aafc5349d9bd83efc56a53a6072_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1053\" data-rawheight=\"189\" data-original-token=\"v2-93f61e1851b49ae1e0f069f1386e0f38\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-1728e5031baddf81c0c9183b94088d19_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1053\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-79b74aafc5349d9bd83efc56a53a6072_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1053&#39; height=&#39;189&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1053\" data-rawheight=\"189\" data-original-token=\"v2-93f61e1851b49ae1e0f069f1386e0f38\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-1728e5031baddf81c0c9183b94088d19_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1053\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-79b74aafc5349d9bd83efc56a53a6072_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-79b74aafc5349d9bd83efc56a53a6072_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"ZDYJyX9J\">阅读词汇占大头，只需要看英文反应中文即可。很多阅读单词你不需要会写，写作用不上的。比如：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8a2d8f9231c2c6470cb5232910f45cb4_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1227\" data-rawheight=\"479\" data-original-token=\"v2-f893720b484cbf461ecfdca7a027451f\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-17145e32263b10e0a9790a8d76344d7c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1227\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-8a2d8f9231c2c6470cb5232910f45cb4_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1227&#39; height=&#39;479&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1227\" data-rawheight=\"479\" data-original-token=\"v2-f893720b484cbf461ecfdca7a027451f\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-17145e32263b10e0a9790a8d76344d7c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1227\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-8a2d8f9231c2c6470cb5232910f45cb4_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8a2d8f9231c2c6470cb5232910f45cb4_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5b02677531fbddf980cba37c4b11edbb_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1224\" data-rawheight=\"520\" data-original-token=\"v2-65fec1c7e44228fb5d51c2cf70d12699\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-72ba2037bb1314bd309d8615a20305ad_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1224\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5b02677531fbddf980cba37c4b11edbb_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1224&#39; height=&#39;520&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1224\" data-rawheight=\"520\" data-original-token=\"v2-65fec1c7e44228fb5d51c2cf70d12699\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-72ba2037bb1314bd309d8615a20305ad_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1224\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5b02677531fbddf980cba37c4b11edbb_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5b02677531fbddf980cba37c4b11edbb_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"bC9cEHn0\">然后是语用词汇，主要为那些常用动词，需要掌握它们的各种变形。比如：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-2bb14452aab8c8721bc60a7b39c8cd41_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"626\" data-rawheight=\"563\" data-original-token=\"v2-2c8d1e00a10acd7eccdd346afcacb819\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-ed70a0914d9aea40508339e99ec87977_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"626\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-2bb14452aab8c8721bc60a7b39c8cd41_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;626&#39; height=&#39;563&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"626\" data-rawheight=\"563\" data-original-token=\"v2-2c8d1e00a10acd7eccdd346afcacb819\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-ed70a0914d9aea40508339e99ec87977_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"626\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-2bb14452aab8c8721bc60a7b39c8cd41_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-2bb14452aab8c8721bc60a7b39c8cd41_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"b8m4pxXB\">最后是写作词汇，需要掌握拼写，以及各种常用搭配：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-95fbf677b60ec5440453503a7596b542_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"670\" data-rawheight=\"456\" data-original-token=\"v2-83fca8d9ef166b6d2a6c41c0bdc34e2f\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e3d48ffe6947231070a46913058c4471_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"670\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-95fbf677b60ec5440453503a7596b542_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;670&#39; height=&#39;456&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"670\" data-rawheight=\"456\" data-original-token=\"v2-83fca8d9ef166b6d2a6c41c0bdc34e2f\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e3d48ffe6947231070a46913058c4471_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"670\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-95fbf677b60ec5440453503a7596b542_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-95fbf677b60ec5440453503a7596b542_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-45bdcb71d864498a90da1a354ca3ec35_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"604\" data-rawheight=\"451\" data-original-token=\"v2-9695cd6cbab30982b21f5696f5c1cbf0\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e26fb9ac46c53fb30d78451839330079_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"604\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-45bdcb71d864498a90da1a354ca3ec35_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;604&#39; height=&#39;451&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"604\" data-rawheight=\"451\" data-original-token=\"v2-9695cd6cbab30982b21f5696f5c1cbf0\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e26fb9ac46c53fb30d78451839330079_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"604\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-45bdcb71d864498a90da1a354ca3ec35_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-45bdcb71d864498a90da1a354ca3ec35_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"HYU5COkm\">不难发现，阅读词汇是最多的，且涵盖了其它词汇。所以如果只是为了快速提高分数，题主的方法是行的通的。至于语用和写作，占比的分数没那么高，可以先等阅读提高后再背相关词汇的拼写。</p><p data-pid=\"wxgPWtMB\">我高中的时候也是英语不好，一开始只有及格分多一点。后来掌握了高效的复习记忆方法，才逐步提分，最后高考拿了 138，对我而言可以说是历史最高了。</p><p data-pid=\"7GlVtk2W\">我用的复习工具是 Anki，想要了解，可以看看我的几篇实战教程：</p><p data-pid=\"jU8SRZXH\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/36475725\" class=\"internal\">简单「Anki」英语熟词生义实战</a></p><p data-pid=\"jAT8bWcF\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/34891600\" class=\"internal\">简单「Anki」英语作文词汇实战</a></p><p data-pid=\"Ww1gsA65\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/35688502\" class=\"internal\">简单「Anki」英语作文话题实战</a></p><p data-pid=\"zRIO70uS\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/36788200\" class=\"internal\">简单「Anki」英语词性转换实战</a> </p><hr/><p data-pid=\"qCgk9wjO\">Anki 支持 windows、mac、linux、安卓、苹果等常见设备，并且可以多端同步，走到哪学到哪。</p><p data-pid=\"Q78jQ5u6\">为了帮到有缘人，我写了一份快速上手教程：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/61564332\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2e8a109841199b0a18e70ae7bd16ea66_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1220\" data-image-height=\"535\" class=\"internal\">叶峻峣：B 站 Ankidroid 视频教程与电子书(全平台教程)快速通道</a><p></p>",
